}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Connects a closure to a signal for a particular object.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>instance</code></title>
  <p>the instance to connect to.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>detailed_signal</code></title>
  <p>a string of the form "signal-name::detail".</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>closure</code></title>
  <p>the closure to connect.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>after</code></title>
  <p>whether the handler should be called before or after the
 default handler of the signal.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Returns</code></title>
  <p>the handler id (always greater than 0 for successful connections)</p>
</item>
